properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 10 at 3:08PM MST until February 11 at 11:00PM MST by NWS Billings MT
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds gusting to 60 mph.

* WHERE...Livingston Area and Beartooth Foothills.

* WHEN...From 11 PM this evening to 11 PM MST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Strong crosswinds will make travel difficult along
Interstate 90 from Springdale through Livingston, and on roads
near Nye.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Blowing snow is also possible. Be alert
for reduced visibility and snow-covered roads.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

Additional graphics for this hazard can be found at
http://www.weather.gov/billings

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 11 PM THIS EVENING TO 11 PM MST TUESDAY
